            "id": "https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/convergence/public-private-hybrid-blockchain/",
            "content_html": "<h2 class=\"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_jcKD\" id=\"i-블록체인-개요\">I. 블록체인 개요<a href=\"https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/convergence/public-private-hybrid-blockchain/#i-%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9D%EC%B2%B4%EC%9D%B8-%EA%B0%9C%EC%9A%94\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to heading\" title=\"Direct link to heading\">​</a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>개념<!-- -->\n<ul>\n<li>탈중앙화된 P2P 네트워크를 기반에 합의알고리즘을 통해 무결성을 제공하는 분산 원장 기술</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>배경</li>\n</ul>\n<table><thead><tr><th>도입기</th><th>발전기</th><th>확산기</th><th>정착기</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>디지털자산</td><td>스마트 계약</td><td>프로토콜</td><td>암호화폐/결제</td></tr><tr><td>거래 결제</td><td>지분증명</td><td>인터페이스</td><td>블록체인 기반 서비스 확대</td></tr><tr><td>비트코인 탄생</td><td>이더리움 탄생</td><td>알트코인 탄생</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td>Public</td><td>Private</td><td>Hybrid</td><td>융복합</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2 class=\"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_jcKD\" id=\"ii-구성\">II. 구성<a href=\"https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/convergence/public-private-hybrid-blockchain/#ii-%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to heading\" title=\"Direct link to heading\">​</a></h2>\n<h3 class=\"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_jcKD\" id=\"iii-적용방안\">III. 적용방안<a href=\"https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/convergence/public-private-hybrid-blockchain/#iii-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%EB%B0%A9%EC%95%88\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to heading\" title=\"Direct link to heading\">​</a></h3>\n<table><thead><tr><th>구분</th><th>적용효과</th><th>적용방안</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>공공</td><td>투명성 확보</td><td>토지대장, 투표, 전자시민권 등</td></tr><tr><td>금융</td><td>거래비용 절감</td><td>환전, 송금, 증권, 지급 등</td></tr><tr><td>민간</td><td>가시성 확보</td><td>물류, 유통, 공급망관리 등</td></tr><tr><td>민간</td><td>지적재산보호</td><td>개인 컨텐츠, 음악, 영상 등</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>\"끝\"</p>",
